features: [6 Cube Storage Organizer] Keep your space clutter-free with this charming cube storage bookcase featuring 6 cubes. It offers an ideal solution for storing and displaying various items such as books, framed photos, plants, and decor. With its industrial-chic look and classic beauty, this storage cube organizer seamlessly fits into any living room or bedroom.

[Minimalist & Stable Design] Designed with clean-lined metal frames and natural wood grain shelves, this cube storage bookshelf exudes elegance and rusticity. The chunky shelves (1-inch thickness) and heavy-duty metal frame ensure a stable and wobble-free cube bookcase.

[Durable Material & Dimensions] Crafted from high-grade MDF and long-lasting heavy-duty metal, this cube organizer has an overall size of W 47.24 inches x D 13.58 inches x H 30.12 inches. The rustic wood grain finish adds a touch of character, showcasing the natural grains of the bookcase.

[Support Legs & High Weight Capacity] With high-grade materials and 2 support legs under the bottom shelf, this cube organizer shelf stands stably and securely. Each layer has a maximum weight capacity of 330 lbs, providing ample support for your belongings.

[Easy Assembly] It only takes 30 minutes to assemble the cube bookshelf. The clear instructions, numbered parts, all necessary tools are also included. If you have any questions before and after purchasing, you can email us anytime, we always reply within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, Easy to Assemble, Heavy
reviews.reviewText: This bookshelf came together easily within twenty minutes with the help of my twelve-year-old.The bookshelf is heavy, so it doesn't pose a tipping or collapsing hazard if you put a giant television on top of it. It also has middle footings that support the inner shelves that can't be seen, so it supports weight across the entire piece. The shelves are sturdy, and the overall look of it is industrial chic. I like the faux wood grain finish, too. The company emailed me with tips on assembling prior to getting the bookshelf, and the instructions that it comes with were simple and easy to follow. I highly recommend this bookshelf. It's worth the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Went together in about 1/2 an hour. All parts are clearly marked, excellent instructions, spare hardware included, simple to assemble, looks great, great look for the price, seems sturdy. Can't say enough good things about it. Finally, some manufacturer took things seriously and created something that looks good, easy to assembly, isn't flimsy, and priced right.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Solid and Looks Great
reviews.reviewText: This was so easy to build that I didn't even really need to look at the instructions. In all, it took probably 15 minutes to assemble. This was likely due to building some of their other products though. Like everything else I have purchased from FATORRI, this is well-built, looks amazing, and is relatively lightweight and easy to assemble. I have had no issues with anything I have purchased from them, and they are all packaged securely. Even with the boxes have arrived with puncture or drop marks, there has been no damage to the panels inside. Definitely recommend this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is a terrific product and SO EASY to put together!!! Excellent buy
reviews.reviewText: I was hoping for a nice looking, quality piece that would support our bedroom TV and have space for books and other things. Also, very important to me, was the ease in putting it together. I was really happily impressed with everything!! It looks great and my husband and I put it together in less than an hour... could be done in 30 minutes or less if familiar with assembling things and didn't have a pet jumping in and out of it! The instructions are extremely easy to follow. Main thing is to read everything before each step and do exactly what they ask. It was the best set of directions I've ever had to follow, and I've put a lot of items together, some very complicated. The packaging was great and easy to identify, plus there aren't really a lot of pieces to assemble. The quality is very good. I do have it on carpet vs hard flooring which may make it a bit less stable as the TV on top is probably larger than intended, but don't think there will be an issue. If so, it would not be the manufacturer's fault. It also has items on the bottom of unit to stabilize it in case of uneven flooring. It is exactly what is advertised, and I couldn't be more relieved and happier to have it!! Highly Recommend if you like the description of product as stated on Amazon website!! I will look for other products from this manufacturer in the future when needed.
